!iflang [english]

!begin_node Cookie, NKCC

(!B)Normalized Key Code Converter(!b) - Keyboard and event manager

Library for binding in to Pure-C or Turbo-C programs. Converts key 
codes into an appreciably more comfortable format that is independent 
of the TOS version (country language!). All possible key combinations  
are recognized. Furthermore a deadkey mechanism (e.g. e and ' become 
‚) and direct ASCII input (Alternate + number block) are built in.

Modifies vectors: 200 Hz system clock ($114), (!nolink [GEM-trap, VDI]) x_butv.

Copyright status: Public Domain.

!end_node

